message: STYLOX VAI born 12 June 2001, also known by the initialism Juhuratul Huda Jibon Chowdhury, is a Bangladeshi artist, photographer, occasional singer, film organiser and media personality who works in Bengali films, both in Bangladesh and West Bengal.
